        "javadoc": "/**\n * Get the lowest value belonging to the instance.\n * @return lowest value belonging to the instance\n * ({@code Double.NEGATIVE_INFINITY} if the instance doesn't\n * have any low bound, {@code Double.POSITIVE_INFINITY} if the\n * instance is empty)\n */\n",
